title: Armored Combat Tank Warfare APK
description:
Ever wanted to drive a T-34 or a Tiger tank? Now you can in the best looking online multiplayer Tank game on the Appstore!
Battle with millions of Android users or with your friends in quick death match duels driving a panzer, gain achievements and climb the online leaderboards!
- Finest 3D graphics
- 1 vs 1 online duels
- Real time physics
- Real time shadows
- Destructible buildings
- Game Center
- Achievements

Requires Android: 2.3 and Up

Version: 1.2.2
